{"tid":461965,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"點解美元弱， 兌港元都長期7.8而唔係7.75","createTime":"2017-11-08T06:30:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-15T06:24:45.000Z","uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1d3a7565069534d4c90040fb7f2893fee23b7932","tid":461965,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:30:18.000Z","msg":"點解美元弱， 兌港元都長期7.8而唔係7.75"},{"pid":"e74e674450a1ce6dcd226345946fc373f5aec8e2","tid":461965,"uid":122850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:37:25.000Z","msg":"我都覺，好似專登咁。係咪有咩陰謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4b724d49acdf1276f1d223dda417f1867d16ce","tid":461965,"uid":16949,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:37:34.000Z","msg":"到你中三就知架啦"},{"pid":"6178c2829a237d7f5cb0ec9348cc736add100a8f","tid":461965,"uid":49056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:41:38.000Z","msg":"HK不屬於全球"},{"pid":"1a5c3e405ec0a4c1db401631cf68ce39ee6ed93b","tid":461965,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:53:06.000Z","msg":"高中數m2會教其實匯率同pi有關.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nusd = hkd *2.5pi"},{"pid":"a158ae8b4545f599a33d326f21dd495993bff078","tid":461965,"uid":80176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:55:02.000Z","msg":"香港有外匯外沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770a5061e712884a4b8790a7d1bff841ceb0d8ee","tid":461965,"uid":80176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:55:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港有外匯對沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8cfc0eb8ccf939390b4ac48f6d0d437a901015e9","tid":461965,"uid":41270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T08:31:43.000Z","msg":"咩港元唔係同美元掛勾咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d285c2abd3d6f463c2f8cc770d303950c2f5d003","tid":461965,"uid":28074,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T10:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩港元唔係同美元掛勾咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係掛勾<br />\n不過係香港政府單方面掛勾<br />\n7.85-7.75 係觸發點<br />\n當美元兌港元低過7.75政府會用儲備沽港元<br />\n相反高過7.85 沽美金"},{"pid":"4b38e69ed9aa1348c157cf2407cf6c4022419086","tid":461965,"uid":36716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T10:56:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩港元唔係同美元掛勾咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係掛勾<br />\n不過係香港政府單方面掛勾<br />\n7.85-7.75 係觸發點<br />\n當美元兌港元低過7.75政府會用儲備沽港元<br />\n相反高過7.85 沽美金</blockquote><br />\n唔會喇，其實港幣佢盡力維持係7.8唔郁，7.75 同7.85其實變化好大，<br />\n<br />\n如果佢淨係7.75同7.85先做野，咁咪好易比人追擊，7.75買，7.85賣到7.75又再買又再賣，咁你無限金錢"},{"pid":"8470504b8b55a5d73363e7ddd6924cb0916a370c","tid":461965,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:15:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到你中三就知架啦</blockquote><br />\n好多時都係7.78, 但近半年長期7.8"},{"pid":"de8479ee3795f5518ed24f48d564389e2c3b403a","tid":461965,"uid":152422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T06:18:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>到你中三就知架啦</blockquote><br />\n好多時都係7.78, 但近半年長期7.8</blockquote><br />\n有好多因素影響的....例如如果香港多熱錢，都會高過中間位置，所以有人話如果港匯跌穿7.8 ，可能係熱錢開始走的訊號"},{"pid":"a87a26dbe4b5ad2e09dfab3028eb4b82a95bf4a5","tid":461965,"uid":28074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:13:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩港元唔係同美元掛勾咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係掛勾<br />\n不過係香港政府單方面掛勾<br />\n7.85-7.75 係觸發點<br />\n當美元兌港元低過7.75政府會用儲備沽港元<br />\n相反高過7.85 沽美金</blockquote><br />\n唔會喇，其實港幣佢盡力維持係7.8唔郁，7.75 同7.85其實變化好大，<br />\n<br />\n如果佢淨係7.75同7.85先做野，咁咪好易比人追擊，7.75買，7.85賣到7.75又再買又再賣，咁你無限金錢</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n這是香港聯繫匯率既制度<br />\n所以需要大量外匯儲備嚟Support <br />\n當然重可以透過加/減息去令個匯率穩定<br />\n<br />\n當年97 索羅斯爆左泰國外匯儲備跟住先黎香港"},{"pid":"358e3093d7ac990990c8b03e6622f1d711e59f1c","tid":461965,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:18:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩港元唔係同美元掛勾咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係掛勾<br />\n不過係香港政府單方面掛勾<br />\n7.85-7.75 係觸發點<br />\n當美元兌港元低過7.75政府會用儲備沽港元<br />\n相反高過7.85 沽美金</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n港紙等於美金代幣。因為係代幣，所以會有風險溢價，所以通常外圍大跌個時，日元美金都大升，港紙會跌（風險溢價加大）。相反，個市好，港紙表現會強過美金（溢價宿小）。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60cdc3e6a4878c57c22d5f056c0b5d31ecb205e7","tid":461965,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:36:43.000Z","msg":"樓上咁多人得一個先講到可能性"},{"pid":"0b74398f8c5f72c487dee729f841cc55db573e19","tid":461965,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:39:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/09/183945_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F09%2F183945_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=14d46683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/09/183950_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F09%2F183950_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=4b463cca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"663b5088d5a0ae5ebbd74f71fda05cd81a7f293d","tid":461965,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T06:24:45.000Z","msg":"有冇高手"}]}